ina}}\n| Ontario\n\n|-\n| 39\n|Eva Carrier<ref>{{cite news | access-date=26 April 2019 | url=https://www.lesoleil.com/actualite/bientot-111-ans-et-pas-de-cellulite-d4cd076638e6ba844729b3261c8eee7e | title=Bient\u00f4t 111 ans et \"pas de cellulite\" | date=7 April 2019 | last=Fabri\u00e8s | first=C\u00e9line | newspaper=[[Le Soleil (Quebec)|Le Soleil]]}}</ref>\n|align=center|F\n| 29 April 1908\n|22 November 2019\n|111 years, 234 days\n|Quebec\n|Quebec\n\n|-\n|40\n|Marie-Louise Meunier<ref name=\"Supercentenarians who lived in Canada\" />\n|align=center|F\n|15 March 1887\n|24 October 1998\n|111 years, 223 days\n|Quebec\n|Quebec\n\n|-\n|41\n|Evangeline Saulnier<ref name=\"Supercentenarians who lived in Canada\" />\n|align=center|F\n|11 September 1890\n|19 March 2002\n|111 years, 189 days\n|New Brunswick\n|New Brunswick\n\n|-\n|42\n|Ethel Lyman<ref name=\"Supercentenarians who lived in Canada\" />\n|align=center|F\n|8 June 1880\n|9 December 1991\n|111 years, 184 days\n|Ontario\n|Quebec\n\n|-\n|43\n|Marie Bibeault<ref name=\"Supercentenarians who lived in Canada\" />\n|align=center|F\n|31 January 1882\n|29 July 1993\n|111 years, 179 days\n|Quebec\n|Quebec\n\n|-\n|44\n|Louise Gibson<ref name=\"Supercentenarians who lived in Canada\" />\n|align=center|F\n|7 August 1883\n|2 January 1995\n|111 years, 148 days\n|Nova Scotia\n|United States\n\n|-\n|45\n|[[George Frederick Ives]]<ref name=\"Supercentenarians who lived in Canada\" />\n|align=center|M\n|17 November 1881\n|12 April 1993\n|111 years, 146 days\n|United Kingdom\n|British Columbia\n\n|-\n|46\n|Lillian Cornell<ref name=\"GRG\" />\n|align=center|F\n|21 August 1904\n|11 January 2016\n|111 years, 143 days\n|United Kingdom\n|Saskatchewan\n\n|-\n|47\n|Sarah Harper<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/sarah-harper-elder-death-1.4453304 | title=Manitoba Cree elder Sarah Harper dies at 111 | publisher=CBC News | date=December 17, 2017 | accessdate=5 December 2018}}</ref>\n|align=center|F\n|24 August 19