lie Gamble]]\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Paul Geddes]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Lenny Glover]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fansonline.net/leicestercity/article.php?id=607|title=Bentleys Roof - Bentleys Roof Message Board|first=Bentleys|last=Roof|date=|website=www.fansonline.net|accessdate=21 April 2018}}</ref>\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Neil Grewcock]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Kevin Hector]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thelinnets.co.uk/matchreports/ln301082.shtml|title=Shepshed Charterhouse v King's Lynn 30/10/82 (FA Cup)|author=|date=|website=www.thelinnets.co.uk|accessdate=21 April 2018}}</ref>\n*{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Terry Hennessey]] (Player/Manager)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mick Hollis]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Liam Hurst]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Gary Ingham]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Julian Joachim]]\n\n{{col-2}}\n*{{flagicon|NIR}} [[Jon McCarthy]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mytimeinfootball.com/Jon_McCarthy|title=Jon McCarthy: My Time In Football|author=|date=|website=mytimeinfootball.com|accessdate=21 April 2018}}</ref>\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ernie Moss]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[David Nish]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.englandfootballonline.com/TeamPlyrsBios/PlayersN/BioNishDJ.html|title=England Players - David Nish|author=|date=|website=www.englandfootballonline.com|accessdate=21 April 2018}}</ref>\n*{{flagicon|NIR}} [[Martin O'Neill]] (Manager)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Levi Porter]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jon Stevenson]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Steve Powell]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[John Ramshaw]] (Manager)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Dean Smith (footballer, born 1958)|Dean Smith]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ian Storey-Moore]] (Player/Manager)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Colin Tartt]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Simon Woodhead]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Frank Wignall]] (Manager)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nottinghampost.com/Wignall-s-broken-leg-ends-World-Cup-bid/story-17903049-detail/story.html|title=Wignall's broken leg ends World Cup bid|author=|date=|website=nottinghampost.com|accessdate=21 April 2018}}</ref>\n*{{flagicon|ENG}}